// CBSE Class 12 Chemistry — question bank (~300 questions, 30 per chapter).
// NCERT-based, modeled on the pattern/topics of recent CBSE board papers.
// Each question: { id, topic, difficulty, q, options: [4], correct: index, solution }
// Difficulty spread per chapter: 10 Easy, 10 Medium, 10 Hard.
// To grow the app, add more objects following the same shape.

